{"TopicId":137043,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Pod race in Kerbin","CreatedByName":"Papahemmy","CreatedById":160877,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T03:27:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Papahemmy","CreatedById":160877,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T03:27:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a idea I thought would be fun. Pod racers on Kerbin. So the challenge is make a working fast pod racer. but here are my only rules:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo mods, cheats, or hacks,\u00A0It needs to go fast (at least 60m/s),\u00A0It needs to look like the basic Idea of a pod racer , and you\u00A0can \u003Cu\u003Eonly\u003C/u\u003E use jet engines no rockets. Also you can use wheels since there aren\u0027t any hover thrusters. And a way that you can have tons of fuel and not have it show is by putting a bunch of small fuel tanks and using the\u00A0\u003Cu\u003EOffset tool\u003C/u\u003E\u00A0to move the tanks into a spot where they don\u0027t show. And I recommend that you use air brakes to steer you pod racer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a couple pictures of what I made so you can get the idea of what to make\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb style=\u0022font-weight:normal;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00222c0fiP0LJ1RvN9JFN9R48hPs8GIxi0dd5GyGfGZw\u0022 height=\u0022351\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/2c0fiP0LJ1RvN9JFN9R48hPs8GIxi0dd5GyGfGZwDlOFOtkJ1QKmz4wl6JEIbZ3POkV_iUxwn2nELuGKopVPjOa2esDJxr9ZmS0fim9UYgkVPpM4Rka1gxOiSauB6ThtfFlBXbSO\u0022 style=\u0022border:none;\u0022 width=\u0022624\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb style=\u0022font-weight:normal;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022X9qx9iM_e9-mAPGPtOXnDNqkKSa_TxJeo_vNYMrm\u0022 height=\u0022351\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/X9qx9iM_e9-mAPGPtOXnDNqkKSa_TxJeo_vNYMrmSx8crCJbBNoNbk7t5YsTi1tZqNlz1hn3pHmNKEiO107DxhXhA3GTym5mBq6a0Y6A8J9TKccSJqWVmEUvEzhYCjA6fcfHnuY8\u0022 style=\u0022border:none;\u0022 width=\u0022624\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent;\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont color=\u0022#000000\u0022 face=\u0022Arial\u0022 style=\u0022font-weight:normal;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.6667px;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003ESo feel free \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003Cfont color=\u0022#000000\u0022 face=\u0022Arial\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.6667px;line-height:23.4667px;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003Ecomment\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003Cfont color=\u0022#000000\u0022 face=\u0022Arial\u0022 style=\u0022font-weight:normal;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.6667px;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003E back and post pictures of your epic pod racers\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-16T03:31:32Z\u0022 title=\u002204/16/2016 03:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Papahemmy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eto it more understandable\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbalScience","CreatedById":161636,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T03:54:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwowz gonna do dat when get full version!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Papahemmy","CreatedById":160877,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T16:42:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a new design I whipped\u00A0\u00A0up this morning\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb style=\u0022font-weight:normal;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg height=\u0022351\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/J9HCvHsK7mK1hvXybGneypmArmnzA9Xw50U8N8Fja_IzbZEf1hAwSI9o3-l33934Vu6GnikPM9P6dlZbBcM9P1Q-m0MwS-YKkEW3MXSBBRvEzkSrcvawpr1sVTg1tw1ztvtiKj7p\u0022 style=\u0022border:none;\u0022 width=\u0022624\u0022 alt=\u0022J9HCvHsK7mK1hvXybGneypmArmnzA9Xw50U8N8Fj\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-16T22:44:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI got a bit bored so I figured I\u0027d build a Pod Racer for this although I did end up attaching some \u003Cs\u003Efrikkin\u0027 laser beams\u003C/s\u003E guns to it and ran a 1 vs 1 against itself using BD Armory just for the hell of it ... I was bored after all \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can watch the video \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/Sp72tW0bFLo\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EHERE\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/dGLTs/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-16T22:45:22Z\u0022 title=\u002204/16/2016 10:45  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DoctorDavinci\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T04:46:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGot 1 in 1.1 doing 191 m/s around the KSC. It can\u0027t fly, but it can pull 5-gee turns using differential thrust. Basically, it uses the (unfortunately extremely fragile) small landing gears with friction control set to 0.0 as omnidirectional wheels, and has 2 Wheesleys. I\u0027m considering building something using KOS that actually does hover by a combination of precisely-controlled allmoving wings (for efficiency) and hover jets (for low-speed hover capability), but that takes time.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nEDIT: switched gear to the heavier but better LY-10\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T05:13:49Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 05:13  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T05:29:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy first racer. The wires are semi-rigid. They stay taught mostly unless you use differential thrust for extended periods while not moving, in which case, Gods have mercy on you. (actually, not really, it\u0027s almost impossible to get killed by this thing, even at 200\u002B m/s. The wires breaking gives you time to slow below 80, which is the toughness of the \u0022cockpit\u0022 The only easy way to kill yourself with it is ramming into water or possibly a brick wall).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ySQhxme.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022ySQhxme.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UZFtAg7.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022UZFtAg7.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/IH7H9Wy.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022IH7H9Wy.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSide view\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T05:29:35Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 05:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T06:08:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnnoyingly, it seems to have landing\u003Cs\u003E gear dragging issues\u003C/s\u003E [EDIT: over-stressing the landing gears] above ~260 m/s that cause instant disintegration.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNvm, just got the issues at 250...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nHmm.. looks like 250 with no SAS, 260 with SAS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n10 Gee turns!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Vs0kRuP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Vs0kRuP.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nLOL: When \u0022Operational limits\u0022 means \u0022The landing gear is bouncing between 88-96% stress.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T06:28:56Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 06:28  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T06:39:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70014-pds314/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002270014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70014-pds314/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Pds314\u003C/a\u003E - You gotta strap some \u003Cs\u003Efrikkin\u0027 laser beams\u003C/s\u003E guns to that beast \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen 1.1 is officially released perhaps we can start a Pod Fighter challenge \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T06:42:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519848\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460961582\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70014-pds314/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002270014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70014-pds314/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Pds314\u003C/a\u003E - You gotta strap some \u003Cs\u003Efrikkin\u0027 laser beams\u003C/s\u003E guns to that beast \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen 1.1 is officially released perhaps we can start a Pod Fighter challenge \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the ground? We would need to have KOS scripts or something, or a BDA AI patch that allows ground vehicles to fight.\u00A0In the air, that might work. Although I feel like in either case it takes a lot more effort to make a podracer win than to make a winning craft that fits the spirit of the rules.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n(Also, if you think fighters make some stupid maneuvers under AI piloting, ground craft moving at a good fraction of the speed of sound would probably be incredibly self-destructive).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T06:44:59Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 06:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T06:44:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519850\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460961779\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pds314\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Pds314 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the ground? We would need to have KOS scripts or something, or a BDA AI patch that allows ground vehicles to fight.\u00A0In the air, that might work. Although I feel like in either case it takes a lot more effort to make a podracer win than to make a winning craft that fits the spirit of the rules.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the air of course ... you saw the video of my POD, it flies (and it shoots \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T06:45:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519851\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460961877\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the air of course ... you saw the video of my POD, it flies (and it shoots \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould work. We\u0027d probably have to make sure entries were... PODly enough, since again, strap allmoving surfaces on the back, use a way overbuild connecting rod with wings on it, and add some wings to the front and it becomes a somewhat unconventional-looking normal fighter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T06:48:17Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 06:48  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T06:47:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519853\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460961954\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pds314\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Pds314 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould work. We\u0027d probably have to make sure entries were... PODly enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGotta be a Pod Racer first, then you strap frikkin\u0027 laser beams on it\u0027s head lol ... form follows function\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T07:01:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022D17BBie.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/D17BBie.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nLanding gear no longer under any stress. 286.3 m/s\u00A0on the outer rim of the southern ice sheet. 300.5 if the Kerbal is removed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T07:04:29Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 07:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"max_creative","CreatedById":159640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T20:42:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! I\u0027m sending pod racers to Dres so there will be the first ever Dres canyon race! Any advice steering in a vacuum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-19T01:23:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222520941\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461012146\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022max_creative\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, max_creative said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! I\u0027m sending pod racers to Dres so there will be the first ever Dres canyon race! Any advice steering in a vacuum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave way more fuel than you think you\u0027ll need.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-19T02:01:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222520941\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461012146\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022max_creative\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, max_creative said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! I\u0027m sending pod racers to Dres so there will be the first ever Dres canyon race! Any advice steering in a vacuum?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll have to use LFO tanks to make it work since there\u0027s no air on Dres .... for steering you could use Vernors\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"max_creative","CreatedById":159640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-19T02:03:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am still having a hard time steering because on no air resistance. I\u0027ve been trying to use rear facing vernors, but it\u0027s really hard to steer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-19T05:25:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222521434\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461031408\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022max_creative\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, max_creative said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am still having a hard time steering because on no air resistance. I\u0027ve been trying to use rear facing vernors, but it\u0027s really hard to steer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could use Gimballing rocket motors, or do what I did and use action groups for differential thrust.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}